---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Info - Purple Trope">
	<div class="InfoPage">
		<div class="InfoHeader">
			<h1>INFO</h1>
		</div>
		
		<div class="InfoContent">
			<p>Purple Trope is more than an art house—it's a living canvas of ideas, design, and storytelling. Founded in 2015 by artist & designer Debjani Hazarika, Purple Trope blends contemporary art, sustainable design, and cultural narratives from Northeast India into creations that inspire thought and conversation.</p>
			
			<p>From bespoke artworks and journals to sustainable gift boxes, visual communication projects, and exhibitions, Purple Trope thrives at the intersection of art, culture, and conscious living.</p>
			
			<p>Debjani's journey is a constant exploration of form and feeling—bringing together doodles, modern design, and cultural symbolism to craft works that not only capture attention but also evoke reflection and joy.</p>
			
			<p>Her vision continues through Purple Trope Archive, where art meets sustainability, offering journals, tote bags, calendars, and thoughtfully designed objects for everyday inspiration.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.InfoPage {
		background-color: #EFEFF2;
		min-height: 100vh;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.InfoHeader {
		padding: 150px 0 20px 50px;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.InfoHeader h1 {
		font-family: 'Kommissar', Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 150px;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: #000;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 0.8;
	}

	.InfoContent {
		padding: 20px 50px 50px;
		max-width: 800px;
		font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 18px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #333;
	}

	.InfoContent p {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
		.InfoHeader {
			padding: 120px 0 15px 30px;
		}

		.InfoHeader h1 {
			font-size: 120px;
		}

		.InfoContent {
			padding: 15px 30px 30px;
			font-size: 16px;
		}
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
		.InfoHeader {
			padding: 100px 0 10px 20px;
		}

		.InfoHeader h1 {
			font-size: 60px;
		}

		.InfoContent {
			padding: 10px 20px 20px;
			font-size: 14px;
		}
	}
</style>
